            Scalability
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 font-normal text-base/7 text-black">
            Built-in solvers with optimized data structures and algorithms
            handle complex models efficiently, yet maintain a biologically
            meaningful view for the user
          </dd>
        </div>
